<dl id="n09008c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n09" href="#n09008c">N09 (VI.B.1)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n09all.htm#n09008c"> 8(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> spiked coat / white vest</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Philadelphia, Feb. 9. <font color="green">[&hellip;]</font> <br>&ldquo;It&apos;s a violation of the law to carry liquor on the hip,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;It&apos;s a violation to serve it at tables or carry it to hotel rooms, and it&apos;s got to stop. <br>&ldquo;We&apos;re going to have a dress suit squad to see that the warning is backed up properly.&rdquo; &ldquo;This squad,&rdquo; he continued, &ldquo;will be made up of men who will look as if they are used to a <mark>spiked coat and a standupcollar and white vest</mark>, and they are going to circulate among the guests of hotels, clubs and cabarets, on the lookout for infractions.&rdquo; <small> <a name="BDJ9feb24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#BDJ9feb24"><cite title="source">Biddeford Daily Journal</cite></a> (e February 1924) GLAD RAGS FOR DRY COPS IN QUAKER TOWN</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
